Package fr.gouv.finances.dgfip.xemelios.common.config Description

Provides classes needed to carry and manipulate documents' configurations. Each tag is mapped to a class, each attribute is a class property. See configuration schema.
See Also:
fr.gouv.finances.cp.utils.xml.marshal
